---
import Base from '../../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Promise - mtdnot blog" description="How this blog is written.">
  <article class="promise-page">
    <h1>Promise</h1>
    <p>AI was used to implement this blog.</p>
    <p>However, I try not to have AI write the substance of the blog itself.</p>
    <p>The content should be thought through and written in my own words.</p>
  </article>
</Base>

<style>
  .promise-page {
    max-width: 720px;
  }

  .promise-page h1 {
    font-size: 1.8rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
  }

  .promise-page p {
    color: #b8b8b8;
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }
</style>
